snippet.title: Melissa Rivers: Joan Rivers' Death Was ‘100% Preventable’ | TODAY
snippet.description:
Melissa Rivers, daughter of the late comedy legend Joan Rivers, sits down with Matt Lauer to describe what she says led to her mother’s death.
